docs.lead_paragraph: At the weekly meeting on last Tuesday afternoon of the Political Study Club, the paper of the day was read by Dr. M.F. Abrams on the subject, "Tenement and Lodging Houses." A discussion followed in which Drs. White and Gunn, Mrs. Blake, Dr. Phoebe Hanaford, and others took part.
